        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><em>Ethereal jaunt</em> at will. He patrols the keep from the Ethereal Plane, watching through Togomor's eyes — and deliberately <strong>lets the PCs kill</strong> the castle's devils, the false queen, even Togomor, to learn their tactics before he manifests. (The Sunken Queen's ghost-touch walls would bar this trick; the castle's do not.)</p>"
